Text: When installing on Windows 8, there is a pause with this windows which says "Restarting the print spooler service..." followed by an error message which says "An error occurred in Windows (MyStartService failed) -- timed out waiting for service" When OK is clicked on in the error message box, installation continues with a final message which says "FinePrint was successfully installed" The opportunity to enter a serial number does not present itself. Go and sort it out please.

@baldiepie
